"Moojo Network" refers to the platform operated by Moojo where user activities are uploaded.

3. Acceptance of Terms
By interacting with the Service, you confirm that you have read, understood, and agree to these Terms and our Privacy Policy.

4. Description of Service
The Service allows Users to:
- Connect their Fitbit account.
- Retrieve activity data from Fitbit.
- Upload activity data to the Moojo Network.
- Receive notifications and messages based on their activity data.

